# GEMINI_API_KEY is server-only (Worker). Do not put it in the frontend bundle.
#
# Local dev (optional — same name as Cloudflare):
#   Project root `.dev.vars` (gitignored) — see `.dev.vars.example`
#   Or `GEMINI_API_KEY` in `.env.local` (gitignored)
#
# Production / preview deploy:
#   One-time: npx wrangler secret put GEMINI_API_KEY
#   Or Dashboard → Workers & Pages → your worker → Settings → Variables and Secrets
#   `npm run deploy` strips any `.dev.vars` copied into dist/ before upload.

# APP_URL: The URL where this applet is hosted.
# AI Studio automatically injects this at runtime with the Cloud Run service URL.
# Used for self-referential links, OAuth callbacks, and API endpoints.
APP_URL="MY_APP_URL"
